{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":960,"text":"I was a new mother"},{"time":3200,"text":"and a young rabbi"},{"time":4480,"text":"in the spring of 2004"},{"time":6360,"text":"and the world was in shambles."},{"time":9240,"text":"Maybe you remember."},{"time":10520,"text":"Every day, we heard devastating reports\nfrom the war in Iraq."},{"time":13680,"text":"There were waves of terror\nrolling across the globe."},{"time":17560,"text":"It seemed like humanity\nwas spinning out of control."},{"time":21000,"text":"I remember the night that I read"},{"time":22880,"text":"about the series of coordinated bombings"},{"time":25040,"text":"in the subway system in Madrid,"},{"time":27760,"text":"and I got up and I walked over to the crib"},{"time":29840,"text":"where my six-month-old baby girl"},{"time":32280,"text":"lay sleeping sweetly,"},{"time":34160,"text":"and I heard the rhythm of her breath,"},{"time":36520,"text":"and I felt this sense of urgency\ncoursing through my body."},{"time":40120,"text":"We were living through a time\nof tectonic shifts in ideologies,"},{"time":44200,"text":"in politics, in religion, in populations."},{"time":46880,"text":"Everything felt so precarious."},{"time":49480,"text":"And I remember thinking,"},{"time":50760,"text":"\"My God, what kind of world\ndid we bring this child into?"},{"time":54960,"text":"And what was I as a mother\nand a religious leader"},{"time":58040,"text":"willing to do about it?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":62840,"text":"Of course, I knew it was clear"},{"time":65640,"text":"that religion would be\na principle battlefield"},{"time":68560,"text":"in this rapidly changing landscape,"},{"time":71040,"text":"and it was already clear"},{"time":72760,"text":"that religion was a significant\npart of the problem."},{"time":76120,"text":"The question for me was,"},{"time":77400,"text":"could religion\nalso be part of the solution?"},{"time":80480,"text":"Now, throughout history,"},{"time":82120,"text":"people have committed\nhorrible crimes and atrocities"},{"time":85360,"text":"in the name of religion."},{"time":88160,"text":"And as we entered the 21st century,"},{"time":90640,"text":"it was very clear that religious extremism\nwas once again on the rise."},{"time":95760,"text":"Our studies now show"},{"time":97040,"text":"that over the course\nof the past 15, 20 years,"},{"time":100320,"text":"hostilities and religion-related violence"},{"time":102480,"text":"have been on the increase\nall over the world."},{"time":105440,"text":"But we don't even need\nthe studies to prove it,"},{"time":107720,"text":"because I ask you,\nhow many of us are surprised today"},{"time":110920,"text":"when we hear the stories\nof a bombing or a shooting,"},{"time":114720,"text":"when we later find out\nthat the last word that was uttered"},{"time":117560,"text":"before the trigger is pulled\nor the bomb is detonated"},{"time":120400,"text":"is the name of God?"},{"time":122040,"text":"It barely raises an eyebrow today"},{"time":124720,"text":"when we learn that yet another person"},{"time":126680,"text":"has decided to show his love of God"},{"time":129240,"text":"by taking the lives of God's children."},{"time":132680,"text":"In America, religious extremism"},{"time":135120,"text":"looks like a white,\nantiabortion Christian extremist"},{"time":139680,"text":"walking into Planned Parenthood\nin Colorado Springs"},{"time":142920,"text":"and murdering three people."},{"time":144800,"text":"It also looks like a couple"},{"time":147080,"text":"inspired by the Islamic State"},{"time":148920,"text":"walking into an office party\nin San Bernardino and killing 14."},{"time":153560,"text":"And even when religion-related extremism\ndoes not lead to violence,"},{"time":158400,"text":"it is still used\nas a political wedge issue,"},{"time":161440,"text":"cynically leading people\nto justify the subordination of women,"},{"time":165560,"text":"the stigmatization of LGBT people,"},{"time":168040,"text":"racism, Islamophobia and anti-Semitism."},{"time":172320,"text":"This ought to concern deeply"},{"time":174440,"text":"those of us who care\nabout the future of religion"},{"time":177400,"text":"and the future of faith."},{"time":179640,"text":"We need to call this what it is:"},{"time":182040,"text":"a great failure of religion."}]},{"cues":[{"time":185120,"text":"But the thing is, this isn't even the only\nchallenge that religion faces today."},{"time":192040,"text":"At the very same time"},{"time":193800,"text":"that we need religion\nto be a strong force against extremism,"},{"time":197440,"text":"it is suffering\nfrom a second pernicious trend,"},{"time":200480,"text":"what I call religious routine-ism."},{"time":203840,"text":"This is when our institutions\nand our leaders"},{"time":206440,"text":"are stuck in a paradigm\nthat is rote and perfunctory,"},{"time":210240,"text":"devoid of life, devoid of vision"},{"time":212320,"text":"and devoid of soul."}]},{"cues":[{"time":214520,"text":"Let me explain what I mean like this."},{"time":216920,"text":"One of the great blessings\nof being a rabbi"},{"time":219720,"text":"is standing under the chuppah,\nunder the wedding canopy, with a couple,"},{"time":224400,"text":"and helping them proclaim publicly"},{"time":226680,"text":"and make holy the love\nthat they found for one another."},{"time":229960,"text":"I want to ask you now, though,"},{"time":231920,"text":"to think maybe from your own experience"},{"time":233840,"text":"or maybe just imagine it"},{"time":235280,"text":"about the difference\nbetween the intensity of the experience"},{"time":238200,"text":"under the wedding canopy,"},{"time":239960,"text":"and maybe the experience\nof the sixth or seventh anniversary."}]},{"cues":[{"time":243200,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":245680,"text":"And if you're lucky enough\nto make it 16 or 17 years,"},{"time":249600,"text":"if you're like most people,\nyou probably wake up in the morning"},{"time":252600,"text":"realizing that you forgot to make\na reservation at your favorite restaurant"},{"time":256160,"text":"and you forgot so much as a card,"},{"time":257800,"text":"and then you just hope and pray\nthat your partner also forgot."}]},{"cues":[{"time":261959,"text":"Well, religious ritual and rites"},{"time":264600,"text":"were essentially designed\nto serve the function of the anniversary,"},{"time":268160,"text":"to be a container in which\nwe would hold on to the remnants"},{"time":272200,"text":"of that sacred, revelatory encounter"},{"time":275120,"text":"that birthed the religion\nin the first place."},{"time":277240,"text":"The problem is that after a few centuries,"},{"time":279760,"text":"the date remains on the calendar,"},{"time":282680,"text":"but the love affair is long dead."},{"time":285560,"text":"That's when we find ourselves\nin endless, mindless repetitions"},{"time":289880,"text":"of words that don't mean anything to us,"},{"time":292120,"text":"rising and being seated\nbecause someone has asked us to,"},{"time":295880,"text":"holding onto jealously guarded doctrine"},{"time":298800,"text":"that's completely and wildly out of step\nwith our contemporary reality,"},{"time":302680,"text":"engaging in perfunctory practice"},{"time":305240,"text":"simply because that's the way\nthings have always been done."}]},{"cues":[{"time":310080,"text":"Religion is waning in the United States."},{"time":313600,"text":"Across the board,\nchurches and synagogues and mosques"},{"time":317560,"text":"are all complaining"},{"time":319960,"text":"about how hard it is to maintain relevance"},{"time":324000,"text":"for a generation of young people\nwho seem completely uninterested,"},{"time":328160,"text":"not only in the institutions\nthat stand at the heart of our traditions"},{"time":331840,"text":"but even in religion itself."},{"time":334440,"text":"And what they need to understand"},{"time":337280,"text":"is that there is today\na generation of people"},{"time":340040,"text":"who are as disgusted by the violence\nof religious extremism"},{"time":343920,"text":"as they are turned off"},{"time":345640,"text":"by the lifelessness\nof religious routine-ism."}]},{"cues":[{"time":350440,"text":"Of course there is\na bright spot to this story."},{"time":354960,"text":"Given the crisis of these two\nconcurrent trends in religious life,"},{"time":359280,"text":"about 12 or 13 years ago,\nI set out to try to determine"},{"time":363000,"text":"if there was any way"},{"time":364560,"text":"that I could reclaim the heart\nof my own Jewish tradition,"},{"time":368760,"text":"to help make it meaningful\nand purposeful again"},{"time":371400,"text":"in a world on fire."},{"time":373520,"text":"I started to wonder,"},{"time":374960,"text":"what if we could harness\nsome of the great minds of our generation"},{"time":379120,"text":"and think in a bold and robust\nand imaginative way again"},{"time":383120,"text":"about what the next iteration\nof religious life would look like?"},{"time":386240,"text":"Now, we had no money,\nno space, no game plan,"},{"time":389320,"text":"but we did have email."},{"time":390800,"text":"So my friend Melissa and I\nsat down and we wrote an email"},{"time":394520,"text":"which we sent out\nto a few friends and colleagues."},{"time":397400,"text":"It basically said this:"},{"time":399240,"text":"\"Before you bail on religion,"},{"time":402440,"text":"why don't we come together\nthis Friday night"},{"time":404640,"text":"and see what we might make\nof our own Jewish inheritance?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":409280,"text":"We hoped maybe 20 people would show up."},{"time":411920,"text":"It turned out 135 people came."},{"time":415000,"text":"They were cynics and seekers,"},{"time":417560,"text":"atheists and rabbis."},{"time":419320,"text":"Many people said that night\nthat it was the first time"},{"time":421880,"text":"that they had a meaningful religious\nexperience in their entire lives."},{"time":426200,"text":"And so I set out to do the only\nrational thing"},{"time":428560,"text":"that someone would do\nin such a circumstance:"},{"time":430720,"text":"I quit my job and tried to build\nthis audacious dream,"},{"time":435680,"text":"a reinvented, rethought religious life"},{"time":439520,"text":"which we called \"IKAR,\""},{"time":441760,"text":"which means \"the essence\"\nor \"the heart of the matter.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":444960,"text":"Now, IKAR is not alone"},{"time":447080,"text":"out there in the religious\nlandscape today."},{"time":449640,"text":"There are Jewish and Christian\nand Muslim and Catholic religious leaders,"},{"time":453480,"text":"many of them women, by the way,"},{"time":455800,"text":"who have set out to reclaim\nthe heart of our traditions,"},{"time":459840,"text":"who firmly believe that now is the time\nfor religion to be part of the solution."},{"time":465600,"text":"We are going back\ninto our sacred traditions"},{"time":468080,"text":"and recognizing that all of our traditions"},{"time":470840,"text":"contain the raw material\nto justify violence and extremism,"},{"time":475160,"text":"and also contain the raw material\nto justify compassion,"},{"time":480000,"text":"coexistence and kindness --"},{"time":482440,"text":"that when others choose to read our texts\nas directives for hate and vengeance,"},{"time":487280,"text":"we can choose to read those same texts"},{"time":489920,"text":"as directives for love\nand for forgiveness."}]},{"cues":[{"time":494120,"text":"I have found now"},{"time":495640,"text":"in communities as varied\nas Jewish indie start-ups on the coasts"},{"time":500880,"text":"to a woman's mosque,"},{"time":502800,"text":"to black churches\nin New York and in North Carolina,"},{"time":506480,"text":"to a holy bus loaded with nuns"},{"time":508800,"text":"that traverses this country\nwith a message of justice and peace,"},{"time":513039,"text":"that there is a shared religious ethos"},{"time":515919,"text":"that is now emerging in the form\nof revitalized religion in this country."},{"time":521600,"text":"And while the theologies\nand the practices vary very much"},{"time":525760,"text":"between these independent communities,"},{"time":528480,"text":"what we can see are some common,\nconsistent threads between them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":531920,"text":"I'm going to share with you\nfour of those commitments now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":535800,"text":"The first is wakefulness."},{"time":538040,"text":"We live in a time today"},{"time":539960,"text":"in which we have unprecedented access"},{"time":542480,"text":"to information about every global tragedy"},{"time":545400,"text":"that happens on every corner\nof this Earth."},{"time":547880,"text":"Within 12 hours, 20 million people"},{"time":550600,"text":"saw that image\nof Aylan Kurdi's little body"},{"time":553200,"text":"washed up on the Turkish shore."},{"time":555600,"text":"We all saw this picture."},{"time":558920,"text":"We saw this picture\nof a five-year-old child"},{"time":561280,"text":"pulled out of the rubble\nof his building in Aleppo."},{"time":565160,"text":"And once we see these images,"},{"time":567560,"text":"we are called to a certain kind of action."}]},{"cues":[{"time":570520,"text":"My tradition tells a story\nof a traveler who is walking down a road"},{"time":574960,"text":"when he sees a beautiful house on fire,"},{"time":578520,"text":"and he says, \"How can it be\nthat something so beautiful would burn,"},{"time":582080,"text":"and nobody seems to even care?\""},{"time":584640,"text":"So too we learn that our world is on fire,"},{"time":587760,"text":"and it is our job to keep our hearts\nand our eyes open,"},{"time":591520,"text":"and to recognize\nthat it's our responsibility"},{"time":594080,"text":"to help put out the flames."}]},{"cues":[{"time":596680,"text":"This is extremely difficult to do."},{"time":598760,"text":"Psychologists tell us that the more\nwe learn about what's broken in our world,"},{"time":602560,"text":"the less likely we are to do anything."},{"time":604920,"text":"It's called psychic numbing."},{"time":606520,"text":"We just shut down at a certain point."},{"time":609520,"text":"Well, somewhere along the way,\nour religious leaders forgot"},{"time":613600,"text":"that it's our job\nto make people uncomfortable."},{"time":616920,"text":"It's our job to wake people up,"},{"time":619000,"text":"to pull them out of their apathy"},{"time":621160,"text":"and into the anguish,"},{"time":622640,"text":"and to insist that we do\nwhat we don't want to do"},{"time":626120,"text":"and see what we do not want to see."},{"time":629480,"text":"Because we know\nthat social change only happens --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":631880,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":632960,"text":"when we are awake enough\nto see that the house is on fire."}]},{"cues":[{"time":637760,"text":"The second principle is hope,"},{"time":639720,"text":"and I want to say this about hope."},{"time":641364,"text":"Hope is not naive,"},{"time":643520,"text":"and hope is not an opiate."},{"time":645480,"text":"Hope may be the single\ngreatest act of defiance"},{"time":649560,"text":"against a politics of pessimism"},{"time":651920,"text":"and against a culture of despair."},{"time":654360,"text":"Because what hope does for us"},{"time":656280,"text":"is it lifts us out of the container"},{"time":659080,"text":"that holds us and constrains us\nfrom the outside,"},{"time":662800,"text":"and says, \"You can dream\nand think expansively again."},{"time":666560,"text":"That they cannot control in you.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":669760,"text":"I saw hope made manifest\nin an African-American church"},{"time":672800,"text":"in the South Side of Chicago this summer,"},{"time":675360,"text":"where I brought my little girl,"},{"time":677040,"text":"who is now 13"},{"time":678280,"text":"and a few inches taller than me,"},{"time":680000,"text":"to hear my friend Rev. Otis Moss preach."},{"time":683560,"text":"That summer, there had already been\n3,000 people shot"},{"time":689080,"text":"between January and July in Chicago."},{"time":693040,"text":"We went into that church\nand heard Rev. Moss preach,"},{"time":696160,"text":"and after he did,"},{"time":698120,"text":"this choir of gorgeous women,\n100 women strong,"},{"time":702400,"text":"stood up and began to sing."},{"time":705200,"text":"\"I need you. You need me."},{"time":708360,"text":"I love you. I need you to survive.\""},{"time":711720,"text":"And I realized in that moment"},{"time":713440,"text":"that this is what religion\nis supposed to be about."},{"time":717040,"text":"It's supposed to be about\ngiving people back a sense of purpose,"},{"time":721760,"text":"a sense of hope,"},{"time":723280,"text":"a sense that they and their dreams\nfundamentally matter in this world"},{"time":728240,"text":"that tells them\nthat they don't matter at all."}]},{"cues":[{"time":731760,"text":"The third principle\nis the principle of mightiness."},{"time":734560,"text":"There's a rabbinic tradition\nthat we are to walk around"},{"time":737240,"text":"with two slips of paper in our pockets."},{"time":739560,"text":"One says, \"I am but dust and ashes.\""},{"time":743000,"text":"It's not all about me."},{"time":744720,"text":"I can't control everything,\nand I cannot do this on my own."},{"time":748960,"text":"The other slip of paper says,\n\"For my sake the world was created.\""},{"time":753160,"text":"Which is to say it's true\nthat I can't do everything,"},{"time":757040,"text":"but I can surely do something."},{"time":760160,"text":"I can forgive."},{"time":761840,"text":"I can love."},{"time":763560,"text":"I can show up."},{"time":765080,"text":"I can protest."},{"time":766720,"text":"I can be a part of this conversation."},{"time":769920,"text":"We even now have a religious ritual,"},{"time":772800,"text":"a posture,"},{"time":774040,"text":"that holds the paradox\nbetween powerlessness and power."},{"time":777760,"text":"In the Jewish community,"},{"time":779000,"text":"the only time of year\nthat we prostrate fully to the ground"},{"time":782320,"text":"is during the high holy days."},{"time":784000,"text":"It's a sign of total submission."},{"time":786840,"text":"Now in our community,\nwhen we get up off the ground,"},{"time":789920,"text":"we stand with our hands\nraised to the heavens,"},{"time":793440,"text":"and we say, \"I am strong,\nI am mighty, and I am worthy."},{"time":799080,"text":"I can't do everything,\nbut I can do something.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":803720,"text":"In a world that conspires\nto make us believe that we are invisible"},{"time":808640,"text":"and that we are impotent,"},{"time":810200,"text":"religious communities and religious ritual"},{"time":812960,"text":"can remind us that for whatever\namount of time we have here on this Earth,"},{"time":816600,"text":"whatever gifts and blessings\nwe were given,"},{"time":819080,"text":"whatever resources we have,"},{"time":820840,"text":"we can and we must use them"},{"time":823200,"text":"to try to make the world\na little bit more just"},{"time":825800,"text":"and a little bit more loving."}]},{"cues":[{"time":827920,"text":"The fourth and final\nis interconnectedness."},{"time":830880,"text":"A few years ago, there was a man\nwalking on the beach in Alaska,"},{"time":834160,"text":"when he came across a soccer ball"},{"time":836120,"text":"that had some Japanese\nletters written on it."},{"time":838640,"text":"He took a picture of it\nand posted it up on social media,"},{"time":842000,"text":"and a Japanese teenager contacted him."},{"time":844720,"text":"He had lost everything in the tsunami\nthat devastated his country,"},{"time":848520,"text":"but he was able\nto retrieve that soccer ball"},{"time":851240,"text":"after it had floated\nall the way across the Pacific."},{"time":854280,"text":"How small our world has become."},{"time":857080,"text":"It's so hard for us to remember\nhow interconnected we all are"},{"time":861920,"text":"as human beings."},{"time":864720,"text":"And yet, we know"},{"time":866720,"text":"that it is systems of oppression"},{"time":869440,"text":"that benefit the most\nfrom the lie of radical individualism."}]},{"cues":[{"time":873560,"text":"Let me tell you how this works."},{"time":875400,"text":"I'm not supposed to care"},{"time":877360,"text":"when black youth are harassed by police,"},{"time":879840,"text":"because my white-looking Jewish kids"},{"time":882160,"text":"probably won't ever get pulled over\nfor the crime of driving while black."},{"time":886080,"text":"Well, not so, because\nthis is also my problem."},{"time":890120,"text":"And guess what?\nTransphobia and Islamophobia"},{"time":893320,"text":"and racism of all forms,\nthose are also all of our problems."},{"time":896880,"text":"And so too is anti-Semitism\nall of our problems."},{"time":900360,"text":"Because Emma Lazarus was right."}]},{"cues":[{"time":902080,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":907560,"text":"Emma Lazarus was right\nwhen she said until all of us are free,"},{"time":910920,"text":"we are none of us free."},{"time":912880,"text":"We are all in this together."},{"time":915800,"text":"And now somewhere at the intersection\nof these four trends,"},{"time":919320,"text":"of wakefulness and hope\nand mightiness and interconnectedness,"},{"time":924080,"text":"there is a burgeoning, multifaith\njustice movement in this country"},{"time":928640,"text":"that is staking a claim on a countertrend,"},{"time":930920,"text":"saying that religion can and must be\na force for good in the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":936080,"text":"Our hearts hurt from\nthe failed religion of extremism,"},{"time":940120,"text":"and we deserve more\nthan the failed religion of routine-ism."},{"time":944360,"text":"It is time for religious leaders\nand religious communities"},{"time":948160,"text":"to take the lead in the spiritual\nand cultural shift"},{"time":951560,"text":"that this country and the world\nso desperately needs --"},{"time":955280,"text":"a shift toward love,"},{"time":957440,"text":"toward justice, toward equality\nand toward dignity for all."},{"time":961360,"text":"I believe that our children\ndeserve no less than that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":965360,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":966600,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}